      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/RenderMan_Fractal.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/RenderMan_Fractal.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223633\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Fractal.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"52c6fb6b-f993-4ba4-b9c4-ce0ef194966b\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p>Like all texture style nodes, this node takes a manifold that applies either a 2D placement using UVs or 3D projection to apply a fractal texture. The default behavior, if no manifold is attached, is to apply over P in 3D.</p><p><br/></p><div class=\"section\"><h3 id=\"PxrFractal-InputParameters\">Input Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-SurfacePosition\">Surface Position</h4><p>The noise can be computed based on the <strong>Current Position</strong> or the <strong>Undisplaced Position</strong> (the position of the surface prior to displacement).</p><p>If you want your displacement and shading patterns to match, use the <strong>Undisplaced Position</strong>.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Layers\">Layers</h4><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223612\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrFractal_Layers_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"687399bc-b567-4338-b12a-aff03f7e6513\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223615\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrFractal_Layers_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ff106e08-2c40-4add-b646-c1422669cf0c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223618\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrFractal_Layers_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"169d077b-ffe9-4b23-b70d-75a0639ee6a0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Layers_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605269&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150 1x\"></span></p><p>The number of noise layers used. More layers add successively more noise, creating a more detailed pattern.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Frequency\">Frequency</h4><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_0.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_0.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223624\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrFractal_Frequency_0.5.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ab53ac34-c7e1-4467-8539-f985b7e5ab67\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_0.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_0.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223627\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrFractal_Frequency_1.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"58cbbd07-3d69-4d48-856a-594f12cb4cfc\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223630\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrFractal_Frequency_2.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e66cb996-549a-4d62-878f-c9ca1d4d4169\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223600/PxrFractal_Frequency_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330605664&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=150&amp;height=150 1x\"></span></p><p>Sets the lowest (starting) frequency of the noise layers.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Lacunarity\">Lacunarity</h4><p>The scale used to determine the frequency of each successive layer of noise. Smaller numbers will cause the layers to be more closely spaced in frequency. Larger values will space them further apart.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Dimension\">Dimension</h4><p>The frequency exponent. This value is used to scale the magnitude of each successive layer of noise using the formula1/f^(3-2*Dimension); where f is the frequency of the noise being used for a given layer. It's called dimension since this value relates to the fractal dimension. Bigger values are rougher, smaller values are smoother.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Erosion\">Erosion</h4><p>The frequency exponent range. Negative values will smooth out the low-valued areas, and positive values will smooth the high-valued ones. The frequency exponent specified by the dimension is itself offset as a function of the noise magnitude. This value adjusts that offset. This determines the so-called crossover scale of the fractal. 0 gives a uniform appearance. </p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Variation\">Variation</h4><p>This value controls which particular variation of the appearance you get - without altering the qualities of the appearance determined by the other controls. So, for example, you can use this to animate the appearance by connecting this to Time or create several unique instances of the appearance by setting this to different values.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Mode\">Mode</h4><p>Different ways to modeOp octaves of noise</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-Manifold\">Manifold</h4><p>The manifold over which to apply the noise. Defaults to P.</p><p><br/></p><div class=\"line\"><h3 id=\"PxrFractal-AdjustOutput\">Adjust Output</h3><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-ColorScale\">Color Scale</h4><p>A multiplier for the color values in a texture can be used to adjust brightness or manipulate individual color channels</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-ColorOffset\">Color Offset</h4><p>Apply an offset to the result, shifting the colors of the result</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-FloatScale\">Float Scale</h4><p>A multiplier for the alpha channel, useful when the alpha is used to drive a parameter</p><h4 id=\"PxrFractal-FloatOffset\">Float Offset</h4><p>An offset for the alpha channel, useful when the alpha is used to drive a parameter</p></div></div><h3 class=\"section\" id=\"PxrFractal-OutputParameters\">Output Parameters</h3><h4 class=\"section\" id=\"PxrFractal-resultF\">resultF</h4><div class=\"section\"><p>The result of fractal texture as a float.</p><h4 class=\"section\" id=\"PxrFractal-resultRGB\">resultRGB</h4><p>The fractal texture as a color.</p><p><br/></p></div>"
    }
  },
